get admin users for domain "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
==========================================================================

NAME
----

get admin users for domain - Get the admin for a domain/path combination.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Get the admin for a domain/path combination.

USAGE
-----

` <?php get_admin_users_for_domain( $sitedomain, $path ); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$sitedomain` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Optional. Site domain.
    Default: empty string

 `$path` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Optional. Site path.
    Default: empty string

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `` `(array)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   The network admins

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [1.0](/Version_1.0 "Version 1.0")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`get_admin_users_for_domain()` is located in
`wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

